Suitable for up to 250 users.

Located in a forest, this is a venue with a central dining table for everyone to be reunited and able to talk to each other. There are also chilled meeting areas where workshops can be held and a forest to explore with its known relaxing features. Perfect for a weekend getaway to solidify your teams’ bond.
